  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7422022">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7422022/" class="title-link">探寻中国城市发展独特道路</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7422022"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/104757717/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u104757717-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/104757717/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">浙江赵青新</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2015-03-23"
      class="main-meta">2015-03-23 09:04:49</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7422022_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  <p class="main-title-tip">
                    这篇书评可能有关键情节透露
                  </p>
                  <div class="toggle_review">
