    <div class="main review-item" id="7487187">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7487187/" class="title-link">《中国城市及其文明的演变》书评：中国城市与文...</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7487187"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/39960473/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u39960473-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/39960473/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Captain</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2015-06-01"
      class="main-meta">2015-06-01 12:30:46</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7487187_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  作为拥有五千年历史的文明古国，中国的文明与其他世界文明有着许多迥然不同的特质，中国是一个农耕文明的国家，文明根植于农业和农村，然而农村却无法成为承载农耕文化的基石，农村的资源往往汇聚于城市之中，城市才是文明的载体，从古至今，城市一直是政治、经济、文化的中心...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
